            <li>• Midface descent with malar flattening</li>
            <li>• Nasolabial fold deepening</li>
            <li>• Prior filler/bioestimulator treatment (Modern Face)</li>
            <li>• Seeking natural, vertical rejuvenation</li>
            <li>• Want faster recovery option</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">cancel</span>
            Not Ideal For
          </h3>
